name: Vibrator
tagline: Mmh Vibrator is a Firefox OS open webapp that transforms your phone into a sensual sextoy
body:
### Welcome to Mmh Vibrator!.

Mmh Vibrator! transforms your phone into a sensual sextoy. This is an online version for test.
In a near future, you'll be able to install it from the Firefox OS marketplace!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
